# Balsamiq Wireframes Component Library
# Review Scraper Interface Design
# Generated for Balsamiq Mockups 3

## Project Information
Project: Review Scraper Frontend Interface
Created: 2024
Purpose: Multi-platform review scraping dashboard wireframes

## Component Definitions

### Layout Components

[BrowserWindow]
Type: Browser Window
Properties:
  - Title: "Review Scraper Dashboard"
  - URL: "https://review-scraper.app"
  - Favicon: Yes
  - Width: 1200px (Desktop)
  - Height: 800px

[SidebarNavigation]
Type: Vertical Navigation
Properties:
  - Width: 240px
  - Background: #F3F4F6
  - Items: Dashboard, Scrapers, Reviews, Analytics, Settings
  - Active State: Blue left border
  - Icons: Font Awesome icons

[HeaderBar]
Type: Header/Navigation Bar
Properties:
  - Height: 64px
  - Background: #FFFFFF
  - Shadow: Subtle bottom shadow
  - Elements: Logo, Search, User Menu

### Data Components

[StatsCard]
Type: Card Container
Properties:
  - Width: 280px
  - Height: 120px
  - Padding: 24px
  - Border: 1px solid #E5E7EB
  - Border Radius: 8px
  - Shadow: Subtle
  - Content: Title, Value, Change indicator

[DataTable]
Type: Table/Grid
Properties:
  - Header: Sortable columns
  - Rows: 10 per page default
  - Striped: Yes (alternating colors)
  - Hover: Yes (row highlighting)
  - Actions: Edit, Delete, Export per row
  - Bulk Actions: Checkbox selection

[ReviewCard]
Type: Content Card
Properties:
  - Width: Full width
  - Height: Auto (min 120px)
  - Padding: 16px
  - Border: 1px solid #E5E7EB
  - Border Radius: 6px
  - Content: Rating stars, Review text, Author, Date, Platform badge

### Form Components

[PlatformDropdown]
Type: Dropdown Menu
Properties:
  - Width: 200px
  - Options: Google Maps, Yelp, TripAdvisor, Facebook, Amazon
  - Icons: Platform logos
  - Default: "Select Platform"

[DateRangePicker]
Type: Date Input
Properties:
  - Type: Date range selector
  - Format: MM/DD/YYYY
  - Presets: Today, Last 7 days, Last 30 days, Last 90 days
  - Validation: End date after start date

[ExportOptions]
Type: Checkbox Group
Properties:
  - Columns: Review Text, Rating, Author, Date, Platform, Response
  - Default: All selected
  - Validation: At least one required

### Modal Components

[ExportModal]
Type: Modal Dialog
Properties:
  - Width: 600px
  - Height: Auto (max 80% viewport)
  - Title: "Export to Excel"
  - Buttons: Cancel, Generate Export
  - Sections: Platform, Date Range, Columns, Format

[ScraperConfigModal]
Type: Modal Dialog
Properties:
  - Width: 700px
  - Height: Auto
  - Title: "Configure Scraper"
  - Tabs: Basic, Advanced, Schedule
  - Buttons: Cancel, Save Configuration

[LoadingModal]
Type: Progress Dialog
Properties:
  - Width: 400px
  - Height: 200px
  - Content: Progress bar, Status text, Cancel button
  - Progress: Percentage and estimated time

