### Typography

#### Font Family
- Primary: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif
- Monospace: SF Mono, Monaco, monospace (for code/data)

#### Font Sizes
- Heading 1: 32px / 40px line-height
- Heading 2: 24px / 32px line-height
- Heading 3: 20px / 28px line-height
- Body Large: 18px / 28px line-height
- Body: 16px / 24px line-height
- Small: 14px / 20px line-height
- Caption: 12px / 16px line-height

#### Font Weights
- Light: 300
- Regular: 400
- Medium: 500
- Semibold: 600
- Bold: 700

### Spacing System

#### Base Unit: 4px
- XS: 4px (1 unit)
- SM: 8px (2 units)
- MD: 16px (4 units)
- LG: 24px (6 units)
- XL: 32px (8 units)
- 2XL: 48px (12 units)
- 3XL: 64px (16 units)

#### Component Spacing
- Card padding: 24px (LG)
- Button padding: 12px 24px (MD LG)
- Table cell padding: 16px (MD)
- Modal padding: 32px (XL)
- Form field spacing: 24px (LG)

### Responsive Breakpoints

#### Desktop: 1200px+
- Full sidebar navigation
- Multi-column layouts
- Rich data tables
- Side-by-side modals

#### Tablet: 768px - 1199px
- Collapsible sidebar
- Stacked cards
- Simplified tables
- Centered modals

#### Mobile: 320px - 767px
- Bottom navigation
- Card-only layouts
- Full-screen modals
- Touch-optimized controls

### Animation Guidelines

#### Transition Durations
- Fast: 150ms (micro-interactions)
- Normal: 250ms (hover states, expansions)
- Slow: 350ms (modal openings, page transitions)

#### Easing Functions
- Standard: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
- Deceleration: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1)
- Acceleration: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 1, 1)

### Accessibility Standards

#### Color Contrast
- Normal text: 4.5:1 minimum ratio
- Large text: 3:1 minimum ratio
- Interactive elements: 3:1 minimum ratio

#### Keyboard Navigation
- Tab order: Logical left-to-right, top-to-bottom
- Focus indicators: Visible outline (2px, blue)
- Skip links: Available for main content
- Escape key: Closes modals and dropdowns

#### Screen Reader Support
- ARIA labels: All interactive elements
- Alt text: All images and icons
- Live regions: Status updates and notifications
- Semantic HTML: Proper heading hierarchy

